{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Signature (シグネチャ)","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Glossary/Signature","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><strong>シグネチャ</strong>は状況によって色々な意味を持ちます。<br>\n こちらを参照してください。</p>\n\n<p></p><dl>\n\n    <dt id=\"signature_functions_シグネチャ_関数\"><a href=\"/ja/docs/Glossary/Signature/Function\">Signature (functions) (シグネチャ (関数))</a></dt>\n    <dd><strong>関数シグネチャ</strong> (もしくは型シグネチャ、メソッドシグネチャ) はFunctionやMethodの入力と出力を定義します。</dd>\n\n    <dt id=\"signature_署名_セキュリティ_\"><a href=\"/ja/docs/Glossary/Signature/Security\">Signature (署名 (セキュリティ) )</a></dt>\n    <dd><strong>署名</strong> もしくは<em>デジタル署名</em>とは、メッセージが正当であることを示す protocol です。</dd>\n\n</dl><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"learn_more","title":"詳細情報","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li>Wikipedia の <a title=\"シグネチャ\" href=\"https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/シグネチャ\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">シグネチャ</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"詳細情報","id":"learn_more"}],"summary":"シグネチャは状況によって色々な意味を持ちます。\n こちらを参照してください。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Signature","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Signature","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Signature","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"签名","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/glossary/signature","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/glossary/signature/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/Glossary","title":"MDN Web Docs 用語集: ウェブ関連用語の定義"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Glossary/Signature","title":"Signature (シグネチャ)"}],"pageTitle":"Signature (シグネチャ) - MDN Web Docs 用語集: ウェブ関連用語の定義 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}